{"tid":1205852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盡快到金鐘支援，愛國團體即將混入搗亂","createTime":"2019-06-12T00:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T00:47:09.000Z","uid":105769,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"85a823f8910cc3b72eb2726e81cd4ddf2b4f2b3f","tid":1205852,"uid":105769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T00:11:48.000Z","msg":"深夜收到政務轉告，大會希望上午出席者争取由早上11㸃集合，提早至7㸃左右到場。大會表示希望多些人能搶先佔位。<br />\n<br />\n因是緊急通知，明白要通知出席者確實有困難，所以大會亦表示能早到多少就多少，*爭取盡早到場*。<br />\n<br />\n希望各團體理解，感謝各位付出的努力。<br />\n現在我同張達明先到現場。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：工聯內部群組<br />\n<br />\n相信呢1-2日親中團體都會落金鐘同我地宣戰，有機會班藍絲襯亂打人搶物資，大家要小心！"},{"pid":"9b0f23f028e439587affdcb3d87300000324aadb","tid":1205852,"uid":105769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T00:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ad6bab8f68c14d3ba89c522c3138f23205ea6c","tid":1205852,"uid":105769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T00:16:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a29f83faae40711afba425cae97ea0a13b4256b","tid":1205852,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T00:17:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>推</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"86c925d8bacb092fd8afe584b500b7dba99352b8","tid":1205852,"uid":105769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T00:23:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ffc4bf9a89a9ed284e7ef9ea1c1137c0a348485","tid":1205852,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T00:43:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8de25009f25cd48baaba9f6d0d360927773d5278","tid":1205852,"uid":238673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T00:47:09.000Z","msg":"叫班仆街返鄉下耕田，唔好阻住地球轉"}]}